{"parse":{"title":"Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Eight (TCG)","pageid":348417,"wikitext":{"*":"{{ExpansionPrevNext | prev=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Seven | next=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Nine}}\n{{TCGPromoInfobox\n|setname=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Eight\n|logo=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Eight logo.png\n|symbol=no\n|cards=90\n|period=January 1st, 2026\n}}\n\n'''Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Eight''' is a series of promotional cards released on January 1st, 2026 through [[Play! Pok\u00e9mon|Pok\u00e9mon Organized Play]] events or affiliated products. This features specifically selected cards from the {{TCG|Stellar Crown}} expansion through {{TCG|Mega Evolution}}, including {{TCG|MEE Basic Energies|MEE prints}} of {{TCG|Energy Card|Basic Energy Cards}}. All cards retained their original set number, but are marked with the Play! Pok\u00e9mon logo. Each Booster pack contains 6 cards. Foil cards in this set have Cosmos Holofoil except for {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon ex}} and {{TCG|ACE SPEC card}}s which retain their regular foil patterns.\n\n\n==Card List==\n{{Setlist/header|title=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Eight|bordercol={{grass color}}|tablecol={{grass color}}|cellcol=fff|textcolor=000000|rarity=yes|symbol=no|promo=yes}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolStellar Crown.png|x18px|link=Stellar Crown (TCG)]] 107/142|H|{{TCG ID|Stellar Crown|Archaludon|107}}|Metal||Rare|Standard Set}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolSurging Sparks.png|x18px|link=Surging Sparks (TCG)]] 164/191|H|{{TCG ID|Surging Sparks|Brilliant Blender|164}}|Item||ACE SPEC Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolSurging Sparks.png|x18px|link=Surging Sparks (TCG)]] 176/191|H|{{TCG ID|Surging Sparks|Energy Search Pro|176}}|Item||ACE SPEC Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolSurging Sparks.png|x18px|link=Surging Sparks (TCG)]] 185/191|H|{{TCG ID|Surging Sparks|Precious Trolley|185}}|Item||ACE SPEC Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolPrismatic Evolutions.png|x18px|link=Prismatic Evolutions (TCG)]] 004/131|H|{{TCG ID|Prismatic Evolutions|Budew|4}}|Grass||Common|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolPrismatic Evolutions.png|x18px|link=Prismatic Evolutions (TCG)]] 116/131|H|{{TCG ID|Prismatic Evolutions|Max Rod|116}}|Item||ACE SPEC Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolPrismatic Evolutions.png|x18px|link=Prismatic Evolutions (TCG)]] 129/131|H|{{TCG ID|Prismatic Evolutions|Sparkling Crystal|129}}|Pok\u00e9mon Tool||ACE SPEC Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 027/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|N's Darmanitan|27}}|Fire||Uncommon|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 047/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Iono's Voltorb|47}}|Lightning||Common|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 053/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Iono's Bellibolt ex|53|Iono's Bellibolt}}{{ex}}|Lightning||Double Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 055/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Iono's Kilowattrel|55}}|Lightning||Rare|Standard Set}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 056/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Lillie's Clefairy ex|56|Lillie's Clefairy}}{{ex}}|Psychic||Double Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 067/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Lillie's Ribombee|67}}|Psychic||Rare|Standard Set}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Together.png|x18px|link=Journey Together (TCG)]] 067/159|I|{{TCG ID|Journey Together|Lillie's Ribombee|67}}|Psychic||Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolJourney Toget